1:05:35.568 --> 1:05:37.271
-What did she do?
-Oh, come on, man.

1:05:37.306 --> 1:05:38.503
You know she had to know.

1:05:38.538 --> 1:05:39.768
I don't think
neither one of them

1:05:39.803 --> 1:05:40.769
would have anything
to do with that.

1:05:40.804 --> 1:05:42.111
Oh, come on.

1:05:42.146 --> 1:05:44.641
That's how they do.

1:05:44.676 --> 1:05:46.445
"That's how they do"?

1:05:54.422 --> 1:05:56.191
Alice.

1:06:04.366 --> 1:06:07.202
You didn't have
to make me nothing.

1:06:07.237 --> 1:06:09.171
I wanted to.

1:06:16.345 --> 1:06:17.740
It's good.

1:06:22.813 --> 1:06:25.550
Listen.

1:06:25.585 --> 1:06:28.322
We got to figure out
what you have to do.

1:06:30.623 --> 1:06:34.394
Maybe some woman's home
or some place

1:06:34.429 --> 1:06:35.791
they can help you
get your memory back.

1:06:35.826 --> 1:06:37.397
I haven't lost
my memory.

1:06:37.432 --> 1:06:40.565
-You may think --
-I haven't lost my memory.

1:06:40.600 --> 1:06:44.701
I know exactly who I am
and where I came from.

1:06:44.736 --> 1:06:47.374
These books told me.

1:06:50.709 --> 1:06:53.611
Who are you then?

1:06:53.646 --> 1:06:55.580
I'm me.

1:06:55.615 --> 1:06:57.813
I know, Alice.
I know you Alice.

1:06:57.848 --> 1:07:00.090
But who are you?

1:07:00.125 --> 1:07:03.687
My whole life's
been a lie, Frank.

1:07:03.722 --> 1:07:05.590
Not just part.

1:07:05.625 --> 1:07:08.461
Not the kind of lies

1:07:08.496 --> 1:07:10.760
people tell themselves
to get by.

1:07:12.599 --> 1:07:15.204
The whole thing.

1:07:15.239 --> 1:07:17.173
So, who are you?

1:07:21.344 --> 1:07:23.773
I was a slave, Frank.

1:07:25.645 --> 1:07:27.447
Do you...

1:07:27.482 --> 1:07:28.811
Do you know what
you're saying?

1:07:28.846 --> 1:07:30.483
Do you?

1:07:30.518 --> 1:07:33.255
I know exactly
what I'm saying.

1:07:33.290 --> 1:07:36.390
No, do you? Do you really know
what you're saying right now?

1:07:38.658 --> 1:07:41.395
Listen.

1:07:41.430 --> 1:07:44.662
Alice, I need you
to tell me who you really are

1:07:44.697 --> 1:07:48.567
-or whoever it is --
-I just told you who I was.

1:07:48.602 --> 1:07:50.371
Alice...

1:07:53.706 --> 1:07:56.674
You need to get somebody
that can help you.

1:07:56.709 --> 1:08:00.150
Why can't you help me?

1:08:00.185 --> 1:08:02.416
Because I'm nobody.

1:08:34.714 --> 1:08:36.813
I'm meeting somebody
tomorrow.

1:08:38.685 --> 1:08:40.487
Somebody...

1:08:40.522 --> 1:08:41.917
I knew.

1:08:45.890 --> 1:08:48.693
That's -- That's good.

1:08:48.728 --> 1:08:50.266
That's...

1:08:50.301 --> 1:08:51.861
That's great.

1:08:55.438 --> 1:08:56.602
You...

1:08:56.637 --> 1:08:58.571
You want me to take you?

1:09:00.674 --> 1:09:02.443
I'd like that.

1:09:15.260 --> 1:09:17.623
<i>Through the mirror of my mind</i>

1:09:17.658 --> 1:09:19.856
<i>Time after time</i>

1:09:19.891 --> 1:09:23.992
<i>I see reflections</i>
<i>of you and me</i>

1:09:24.027 --> 1:09:25.961
<i>Reflections of</i>

1:09:25.996 --> 1:09:28.403
<i>The love you took from me</i>

1:09:28.438 --> 1:09:31.835
<i>Oh, I'm all alone now</i>

1:09:31.870 --> 1:09:34.277
<i>No love to shield me</i>

1:09:34.312 --> 1:09:36.675
<i>Trapped in a world that's</i>

1:09:36.710 --> 1:09:41.515
<i>A distorted reality</i>

1:09:41.550 --> 1:09:43.748
<i>Through the mirror of my mind</i>

1:09:43.783 --> 1:09:46.355
<i>Through these tears</i>
<i>that I'm crying</i>

1:09:46.390 --> 1:09:50.326
<i>Reflects a hurt I can't control</i>

1:09:50.361 --> 1:09:52.394
<i>'Cause although you're gone</i>

1:09:52.429 --> 1:09:55.331
<i>I keep holding on</i>

1:09:55.366 --> 1:09:57.366
<i>To the happy times</i>

1:09:57.401 --> 1:10:00.831
<i>Ooh, when you were mine</i>

1:10:00.866 --> 1:10:03.372
<i>As I peer through the window</i>

1:10:03.407 --> 1:10:05.605
<i>Of lost time</i>

1:10:05.640 --> 1:10:07.838
<i>Looking over my yesterdays</i>

1:10:07.873 --> 1:10:13.008
<i>And all the love</i>
<i>I gave all in vain</i>

1:10:13.043 --> 1:10:14.746
<i>All the love</i>

1:10:14.781 --> 1:10:17.980
<i>All the love that I've wasted</i>

1:10:18.015 --> 1:10:19.619
<i>All the tears</i>

1:10:19.654 --> 1:10:22.886
<i>All the tears that I've tasted</i>

1:10:22.921 --> 1:10:30.333
<i>All in vain</i>

1:10:30.368 --> 1:10:32.731
<i>Through the hollow of my tears</i>

1:10:32.766 --> 1:10:35.470
<i>I see a dream that's lost</i>

1:10:35.505 --> 1:10:37.670
<i>From the hurt</i>

1:10:37.705 --> 1:10:40.035
<i>That you have caused</i>

1:10:40.070 --> 1:10:42.444
<i>Everywhere I turn</i>

1:10:42.479 --> 1:10:44.908
<i>Seems like everything I see</i>

1:10:44.943 --> 1:10:48.714
<i>Reflects the love</i>
<i>that used to be</i>

1:10:48.749 --> 1:10:50.947
<i>In you I put</i>

1:10:50.982 --> 1:10:53.719
<i>All my faith and trust</i>

1:10:53.754 --> 1:10:55.457
<i>Right before my eyes</i>

1:10:55.492 --> 1:10:57.426
It's<i> Rolling Stone.</i>

1:11:00.497 --> 1:11:01.991
How do I look?

1:11:02.026 --> 1:11:04.433
Like you.

1:11:04.468 --> 1:11:06.501
<i>Just a handful of promises</i>

1:11:06.536 --> 1:11:11.506
<i>Are all that's left</i>
<i>of loving you</i>

1:11:11.541 --> 1:11:13.409
<i>All the love</i>

1:11:13.444 --> 1:11:16.775
<i>All the love that I've wasted</i>

1:11:16.810 --> 1:11:18.414
<i>All the tears</i>

1:11:18.449 --> 1:11:21.648
<i>All the tears that I've tasted</i>

1:11:21.683 --> 1:11:25.685
<i>All in vain</i>

1:11:32.562 --> 1:11:35.464
You gonna be okay
going to see your friend?

1:11:35.499 --> 1:11:37.862
She was never my friend.

1:11:37.897 --> 1:11:39.930
She ain't your friend?

1:11:39.965 --> 1:11:41.998
That's right.

1:11:42.033 --> 1:11:43.406
How does that work?

1:11:43.441 --> 1:11:45.375
Just does.

1:11:47.445 --> 1:11:48.972
You need me to come with you?

1:11:49.007 --> 1:11:50.545
No.

1:12:01.459 --> 1:12:03.723
Sit anywhere you want.

1:12:14.835 --> 1:12:16.703
Just you?

1:12:16.738 --> 1:12:18.705
I'm waiting on somebody.

1:12:18.740 --> 1:12:20.135
Coffee?

1:12:42.896 --> 1:12:45.930
I-I'm looking for someone,
a woman.

1:12:45.965 --> 1:12:47.536
There's
a lot of women here.

1:12:47.571 --> 1:12:50.099
A Negro woman.

1:12:50.134 --> 1:12:53.201
-Take it easy.
-Take care.

1:12:53.236 --> 1:12:55.808
Alice.

1:12:55.843 --> 1:12:57.480
You look so different.

1:12:57.515 --> 1:12:59.075
You don't.

1:13:07.591 --> 1:13:10.460
Self-seating.

1:13:10.495 --> 1:13:12.088
Sweetie, turn that down.

1:13:13.564 --> 1:13:15.663
He's obsessed with that thing.

1:13:17.502 --> 1:13:20.998
I hid it in his suitcase
when he went to see Paul.

1:13:21.033 --> 1:13:22.604
Any coffee?

1:13:22.639 --> 1:13:24.474
I'm shocked he didn't find it.

1:13:24.509 --> 1:13:25.541
I heard it.

1:13:25.576 --> 1:13:27.070
I'm hungry, Alice.

1:13:27.105 --> 1:13:29.644
I'm not here to serve you.

1:13:31.208 --> 1:13:34.011
Why don't you go
check out that machine

1:13:34.046 --> 1:13:36.915
while mommy talks, okay?

1:13:36.950 --> 1:13:38.081
Alice --

1:13:38.116 --> 1:13:39.918
I'm not afraid of you anymore.

1:13:39.953 --> 1:13:42.525
You should never
have been afraid.

1:13:42.560 --> 1:13:45.792
We always wanted
to provide a safe place

1:13:45.827 --> 1:13:48.058
for our domestics.

1:13:48.093 --> 1:13:49.158
Yes.

1:13:49.193 --> 1:13:50.863
That includes discipline.

1:13:50.898 --> 1:13:53.701
But every home
needs structure.

1:13:53.736 --> 1:13:57.969
Life before people got confused
about their place,

1:13:58.004 --> 1:14:00.675
and it was
a lot less hard --

1:14:00.710 --> 1:14:03.942
I was never confused.

1:14:03.977 --> 1:14:05.614
I was lied to.

1:14:05.649 --> 1:14:06.945
You blame me?

1:14:06.980 --> 1:14:09.112
I always thought of you
as family.

1:14:09.147 --> 1:14:12.049
Stop with the lies,
Rachel.

1:14:12.084 --> 1:14:15.118
My family died
so yours could leave.

1:14:15.153 --> 1:14:16.922
I am not the devil,
Alice.

1:14:16.957 --> 1:14:19.859
No, the devil got to you
long before you left.

1:14:19.894 --> 1:14:21.828
-I am learning every --
-Enough.

1:14:21.863 --> 1:14:24.127
Why'd you ask me here
if I can't talk?

1:14:24.162 --> 1:14:26.701
Because this whole thing,

1:14:26.736 --> 1:14:29.165
me sitting
across from you,

1:14:29.200 --> 1:14:31.871
this ain't about<i> you.</i>

1:14:31.906 --> 1:14:33.906
This is about me

1:14:33.941 --> 1:14:35.237
seeing you

1:14:35.272 --> 1:14:39.043
for exactly what you are.

1:14:39.078 --> 1:14:42.981
Outside of that backwards world
I was born into to believe

1:14:43.016 --> 1:14:45.654
-you were actually somebody.
-Alice --

1:14:45.689 --> 1:14:49.185
I thought if I could see you
out in the open,

1:14:49.220 --> 1:14:51.726
It might stop me
from thinking about hunting down

1:14:51.761 --> 1:14:54.124
and doing something to make sure
you never forget my name.

1:14:54.159 --> 1:14:56.159
-Watch it, Alice.
-But Daniel

1:14:56.194 --> 1:14:58.227
needs at least one parent.

1:14:58.262 --> 1:14:59.228
Alice!

1:14:59.263 --> 1:15:02.770
I'm not scared.

1:15:02.805 --> 1:15:04.838
And that should
scare you --

1:15:04.873 --> 1:15:06.708
-Alice!
-Shut the hell up!

1:15:06.743 --> 1:15:08.809
It's my turn now.

1:15:08.844 --> 1:15:11.108
You left us there to die.

1:15:11.143 --> 1:15:13.979
You watched us
get tormented.

1:15:14.014 --> 1:15:16.047
And you thought
I wanted to meet up with you

1:15:16.082 --> 1:15:19.149
just to hear you talk.

1:15:19.184 --> 1:15:21.657
I don't give a damn
about your life.

1:15:21.692 --> 1:15:23.285
Freedom...

1:15:23.320 --> 1:15:26.057
is something you will never
understand in a million years.

1:15:27.159 --> 1:15:29.159
I<i> am</i> freedom.

1:15:29.194 --> 1:15:30.831
Daniel! Daniel!

1:15:30.866 --> 1:15:32.833
-Alice.
-Frank?

1:15:32.868 --> 1:15:34.703
Daniel, come.
Come.

1:15:34.738 --> 1:15:36.166
-Y'all need to leave.
-Alice, wait. Wait, Alice.

1:15:36.201 --> 1:15:37.365
Hey, hey, hey.
You got a bill.

1:15:42.240 --> 1:15:44.812
-What about Alice?
-Get in the car right now!

1:15:44.847 --> 1:15:48.244
Rachel!

1:15:48.279 --> 1:15:49.278
Don't...

1:15:51.920 --> 1:15:54.151
You let them get away!
Go to hell!

1:15:55.385 --> 1:15:58.089
Alice...

1:16:01.864 --> 1:16:03.358
I have to go back.

1:16:03.393 --> 1:16:05.800
Nah, you can't go back.
What you talking about?

1:16:05.835 --> 1:16:07.329
You know what will happen
to you?

1:16:07.364 --> 1:16:10.772
Everybody that's ever
cared about me is still there.

1:16:12.072 --> 1:16:13.808
I got to get them out.

1:16:16.043 --> 1:16:18.406
I'm'a need some more books.

1:17:25.013 --> 1:17:27.112
<i>What would you do?</i>
<i>Kill all of them?</i>

1:17:27.147 --> 1:17:30.412
<i>Well, why not? Nothing</i>
<i>else seems to do any good.</i>

1:17:30.447 --> 1:17:33.756
<i>You know who they are.</i>
<i>Everybody knows who they are.</i>

1:17:33.791 --> 1:17:36.385
<i>And the law is in</i>
<i>for a piece of the action.</i>

1:17:38.191 --> 1:17:40.895
<i>So, you want to play</i>
<i>with knives?</i>

1:17:42.393 --> 1:17:47.902
<i>You want to spit on me and make</i>
<i>me crawl, white motherfucker?</i>

1:17:47.937 --> 1:17:50.366
<i>Well, you picked</i>
<i>the wrong player.</i>

1:17:50.401 --> 1:17:53.105
<i>It seems like I'm in a dream.</i>

1:17:53.140 --> 1:17:54.942
<i>And I'm still in this dream,</i>

1:17:54.977 --> 1:17:59.782
<i>and it wouldn't take much</i>
<i>for me to kill you now.</i>

1:17:59.817 --> 1:18:02.851
<i>Shit. Look.</i>
<i>I ain't gonna shoot you.</i>

1:18:02.886 --> 1:18:07.284
<i>I'm gonna piss on your grave</i>
<i>tomorrow.</i>

1:18:16.130 --> 1:18:18.031
What'd you think?

1:18:21.333 --> 1:18:23.036
She wasn't real.

1:18:23.071 --> 1:18:25.170
Was she?

1:18:27.042 --> 1:18:30.505
What she believed in,
what she stood for was.

1:18:30.540 --> 1:18:32.474
Right on.

1:18:35.413 --> 1:18:37.820
You said you was going back.

1:18:37.855 --> 1:18:39.789
I am.

1:18:43.025 --> 1:18:45.421
What's going on, Alice?

1:18:45.456 --> 1:18:48.358
I'm going back.
Tomorrow.

1:18:48.393 --> 1:18:51.031
You can't go back by yourself.

1:18:53.299 --> 1:18:55.871
-The police ain't gonna help --
-Police?

1:18:55.906 --> 1:18:57.939
Them folk that's supposed
to help people.

1:18:57.974 --> 1:19:00.909
Well, they help
some people sometimes.

1:19:00.944 --> 1:19:02.438
You can't help me?

1:19:04.915 --> 1:19:08.312
You still do what
your brother tells you.

1:19:08.347 --> 1:19:11.920
So you no different
than me.

1:19:11.955 --> 1:19:15.055
But you used to stand
for something --

1:19:15.090 --> 1:19:17.255
the marches, the sit-ins.

1:19:17.290 --> 1:19:19.796
I saw them
in your memory box.

1:19:21.030 --> 1:19:23.998
Frank.

1:19:24.033 --> 1:19:26.231
What happened to you?

1:19:26.266 --> 1:19:29.366
What happened...

1:19:29.401 --> 1:19:33.040
was I spent
a decade of my life

1:19:33.075 --> 1:19:36.439
trying to help the cause.

1:19:36.474 --> 1:19:38.111
and make a change
for the people.

1:19:38.146 --> 1:19:40.278
That's what
happened to me.

1:19:40.313 --> 1:19:42.247
You know what changed.

1:19:42.282 --> 1:19:45.085
My mother died,

1:19:45.120 --> 1:19:47.417
and I got older,

1:19:47.452 --> 1:19:49.485
and the leaders got killed,

1:19:49.520 --> 1:19:51.223
and everybody
just stopped trying.

1:19:51.258 --> 1:19:53.621
That's what happened.

1:19:53.656 --> 1:19:57.097
But you can
make a change.

1:19:57.132 --> 1:20:01.134
You can make a change now.

1:20:01.169 --> 1:20:04.566
Something that's bigger
than yourself.

1:20:04.601 --> 1:20:06.304
Like Coffy.

1:20:06.339 --> 1:20:08.471
Oh, Alice.

1:20:08.506 --> 1:20:10.473
Oh, no. Just --

1:20:10.508 --> 1:20:15.181
A Black man trying
to do something for hisself.

1:20:15.216 --> 1:20:18.184
Where is that gonna happen
in America?

1:20:18.219 --> 1:20:20.219
That's a death certificate.

1:20:20.254 --> 1:20:23.288
You understand me?

1:20:23.323 --> 1:20:26.324
I'm asking myself
to get killed doing that.

1:20:26.359 --> 1:20:28.194
That's what that is.

1:20:28.229 --> 1:20:31.461
Where is that gonna happen?
You tell me that.

1:20:31.496 --> 1:20:33.265
But you can do something.

1:20:36.237 --> 1:20:38.237
You ain't got
no birth certificate

1:20:38.272 --> 1:20:40.569
or no Social Security, no I.D.

1:20:40.604 --> 1:20:42.945
You -- You can do
what you want.

1:20:42.980 --> 1:20:45.442
I didn't expect you
to say yes,

1:20:45.477 --> 1:20:47.917
but just so you know,

1:20:47.952 --> 1:20:50.645
doing the right thing

1:20:50.680 --> 1:20:53.153
is never wrong.

1:20:56.422 --> 1:20:59.390
I'm wrong because
I can't help you.

1:21:01.064 --> 1:21:02.624
No.

1:21:02.659 --> 1:21:05.693
You're wrong...

1:21:05.728 --> 1:21:08.201
'cause you don't believe.

1:21:10.271 --> 1:21:12.040
Not any more.

1:21:17.212 --> 1:21:19.080
What's your plan?

1:21:28.388 --> 1:21:30.256
We might need these.

1:21:37.727 --> 1:21:40.563
You came out
right about here.

1:21:40.598 --> 1:21:43.269
That's the service road
right there.

1:21:43.304 --> 1:21:46.008
You want
to take the road?

1:21:46.043 --> 1:21:48.472
For what we want to do,
we better.

1:21:50.443 --> 1:21:53.114
Yeah, then everybody
can see the truth.

1:21:53.149 --> 1:21:55.512
What's public transit?

1:21:55.547 --> 1:21:57.349
It's a bus, Alice.

1:21:57.384 --> 1:22:00.352
It pick people up and
take them where they need to go.

1:22:02.554 --> 1:22:05.357
-You sure you want to do this?
-I'm sure.

1:22:07.295 --> 1:22:08.525
Well, tomorrow night,

1:22:08.560 --> 1:22:10.692
if you change your mind
at any time,

1:22:10.727 --> 1:22:12.364
they don't
make you weaker.

1:22:12.399 --> 1:22:15.631
We can figure out
how to get everybody out.

1:22:15.666 --> 1:22:17.435
Like what?

1:22:20.506 --> 1:22:24.409
Well, everything
don't work out as planned.

1:22:24.444 --> 1:22:29.150
I used to dream of breaking
my mom out of that hospital.

1:22:29.185 --> 1:22:31.020
Why didn't you?

1:22:31.055 --> 1:22:33.187
I didn't believe I could.

1:22:34.652 --> 1:22:35.992
Frank.

1:22:37.523 --> 1:22:39.391
I'm not backing out.

1:22:55.706 --> 1:22:57.541
Hello.

1:22:57.576 --> 1:22:58.509
<i> Alice.</i>

1:22:58.544 --> 1:23:00.148
Frank.

1:23:01.745 --> 1:23:03.118
Frank.

1:23:03.153 --> 1:23:05.120
I can't do it.
I can't.

1:23:05.155 --> 1:23:06.748
<i>I just --</i>
<i>I can't do it.</i>

1:23:06.783 --> 1:23:08.750
<i>And, Alice, I don't think</i>
<i>you should do it either.</i>

